### **4. 26_LivePlotScope**  
**Description:**  
Plots a real-time line graph of incoming numeric values using Matplotlib.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LivePlotScope - Streaming Data Chart Renderer

LivePlotScope turns live or simulated numeric input into a dynamic, scrollable chart for monitoring or demos.

## Features
- Real-time scrollable line chart  
- Adjustable frame rate  
- Minimal UI  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/26_LivePlotScope.git
cd 26_LivePlotScope
python visualize.py
